property_description: A private villa awaits you behind the prestigious gates of Vianza at Crocker Ranch. Backing up to a lush Greenbelt, this Tuscan Estate will take your breath away. The formal entry to the first floor & elegant dining areas greet you upon entry. Maple wood floors, spacious family room hosts a fireplace opening to an Italian kitchen with ample counter space, double ovens, 2 new Bosch dishwashers, wine refrigerator & walk-in pantry. Rounding out the the first floor is a powder room, bedroom with an ensuite, and an extended 3 car garage with a workbench & an oversized extended one car garage. Upstairs hosts 3 generously sized bedrooms, 2 full baths, laundry & a generous bonus room with a study area and outdoor balcony. The primary suite is palatial & airy, the primary bath includes two sinks, oversized tub, shower stall & walk-in closet. The backyard takes you to a private tuscan country side with a Greenbelt accompanied by lush landscape, solar-powered salt water PebbleFina pool & built in fountain. Entertain guests with the putting green, outdoor island grill, & relax under the covered gazebo with the wood burning fire place. The estate offers privacy, and is walking distance from several parks, minutes from shopping & restaurants, top rated schools, quick access to Hwy-65 & I80.
